HST=`hostname`; getent passwd  | awk -v hst="$HST" -F:  '{printf (hst"|"$1"|"$3"|"$4"|"$5"|"$6"|"$7"|") ; system(" for gid in `id -G "$1"`; do all_groups=`getent group | cut -f 1,3 -d :`  ;  selected=`for ganame in $all_groups  ; do  echo $ganame | grep :$gid$ | cut -f 1 -d : ; done | tr \"\n\" \" \" `; result=$selected\" \"$result  ; done ; echo $result") }'
